6
0:00:25.632,000 --> 0:00:26,000
It's a type of salamander,

7
0:00:27.13,000 --> 0:00:29,000
but it never fully grows up and climbs out of the water

8
0:00:29.975,000 --> 0:00:3,000
like other salamanders do.

9
0:00:32.178,000 --> 0:00:35,000
And this little guy has X-Man-style powers, right?

10
0:00:35.46,000 --> 0:00:36,000
So if it loses any limb,

11
0:00:37.285,000 --> 0:00:39,000
it can just completely regenerate.

12
0:00:39.544,000 --> 0:00:4,000
It's amazing.

13
0:00:40.719,000 --> 0:00:43,000
