14
0:00:43.859,000 --> 0:00:44,000
(Laughter)

15
0:00:44.889,000 --> 0:00:45,000
It's framed by feathery gills.

16
0:00:46.377,000 --> 0:00:48,000
It's just ... how could you not love that?

17
0:00:48.445,000 --> 0:00:51,000
This particular type of axolotl, a very close relative,

18
0:00:52.381,000 --> 0:00:53,000
